      "text": "[App A] [App B] [App C]\n[Guest OS] [Guest OS] [Guest OS]\n         [Hypervisor]\n           [Host OS]\n           [Hardware]\n\nSize: ~1 GB+ per VM\nStart time: 1-5 minutes",
