    },
    {
      "id": "dockerhdr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 278,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "Docker Workflow",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "dockerbody",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 305,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 138,
      "text": "1. Write Dockerfile (recipe)\n2. docker build -t app:1.0 .\n   -> creates IMAGE (read-only)\n3. docker run -p 3000:3000 app:1.0\n   -> creates CONTAINER (running)\n4. docker push myrepo/app:1.0\n   -> push to Registry (Docker Hub/ECR)\n5. docker pull on any machine -> runs identically",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "k8s",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 270,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "backgroundColor": "#f3d9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "k8shdr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 420,
      "y": 278,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 25,
      "text": "Kubernetes (Production)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "k8sbody",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 370,
      "y": 305,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 138,
      "text": "Orchestrates containers across machines:\n\nDeployment: run 3 replicas\nService: stable network endpoint\nIngress: HTTP routing\nHPA: auto-scale on CPU/memory\n\nMagic:\n- self-heals (restarts crashed pods)\n- rolling updates (zero downtime)\n- auto-scaling up and down",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#6a1e9c",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "tip",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 465,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 50,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ttip",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 472,
      "width": 630,
      "height": 42,
      "text": "Best Practices: Multi-stage builds (small images) | .dockerignore | Layer caching (copy package.json FIRST, then code) | Never SSH into containers -- rebuild and redeploy",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#7c4a00",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    }
